# Lösung

Dekade berechnen:



::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
d <-
  d %>% 
  mutate(decade = round(Year/10))
```
:::



Korrelation:


::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
d %>% 
  summarise(temp_cor = cor(Jan, Feb))
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
# A tibble: 1 × 1
  temp_cor
     <dbl>
1    0.942
```


:::
:::





Korrelation pro Dekade:



::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
d_summarized <- 
  d %>% 
  group_by(decade) %>% 
  summarise(temp_cor = cor(Jan, Feb))
```
:::

